                                </table>
                                <p>The Blackview BV5500 represents another affordable China-made option that packs numerous features under its reinforced military grade chassis. Features include a large 5.5’’ display, powerful battery, polycarbonate construction and Android 8.1 Oreo. This rugged handset is ideal for outdoor workers and hobbyists alike.</p>
                                <h2>Ulefone Armor 6</h2>
                                <img src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/onexone.png"
                                     data-src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/rebrand/blog/most-durable-phones-7.jpg"
                                     alt="Ulefone Armor 6"
