                                <p>Ulefone continues to push boundaries in the durable smartphone sphere, with the Armor 6 neatly encapsulating their forward-thinking engineering.</p>
                                <p>Structurally tough and intelligent within, the latest Armor iteration is perfect for those seeking a durable handset that effortlessly handles the elements. It’s waterproof, drop-proof, shockproof and dustproof – establishing the Armor 6 as a rugged, durable smartphone that’ll accompany you in the most demanding environments.</p>
                                <p>And the features don’t end there. It’s also equipped with a Gorilla Glass Full HD+ display, wireless charging, a dual lens camera, and IP68 certification - making this an affordable, flagship feature rugged smartphone.</p>
                                <h2>Samsung XCover 4</h2>
                                <img src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/onexone.png"
                                     data-src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/rebrand/blog/most-durable-phones-6.jpg"
                                     alt="Samsung XCover 4"
                                     class="img-fluid lozad mb-5">
