                                <p>Traditionally associated with sleek, industry leading designs, Samsung’s latest entry sees the electrical powerhouse take on the rugged smartphone market – and the results are impressive.</p>
                                <p>Despite being the lowest priced phone on our list, the XCover 4 effortlessly blends sophisticated aesthetics with a reinforced construction that meets both IP68 and Mil-STD 810G standards.</p>
                                <p>Aside from its svelte, yet rugged build, the XCover 4 keeps your hands warm and dry during use, thanks to its 100% glove-compatible intuitive display; and you’ll never get caught short while working outdoors, courtesy of its 2800mAh battery.</p>
                                <p>The XCover 4 runs Android’s latest OS, allowing you to install all your favourite apps, while its sophisticated dual camera lets you capture those special moments at the touch of a button.</p>
                                <h2>OnePlus 5T</h2>
                                <img src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/onexone.png"
