                                <p>If you’re looking for a smartphone that isn’t quite military grade but will still be around for the long haul, the OnePlus 5T is our go-to handset. Featuring heat and scratchproof Gorilla Glass 5 and a hard aluminium oxide exterior, the 5T resists bends, bumps and scratches, so you can rest assured it won’t get damaged in your pocket. One thing you should bear in mind, however, is that this handset’s not waterproof. But don’t let that put you off, as we offer specialist cover for the <a href="{{ path('phone_insurance_make_model', {'make': 'OnePlus', 'model': '5T'}) }}">OnePlus 5T</a> that covers against accidental damage as well as theft.</p>
